body:
**No** change in default behavior.
This PR includes:
-new MF geometry XML files;
-cleanup obsolete download.url files;
-update tools for table conversion and for generation of .db payloads for MF geometry and configuration;
-update validation, field visualization and regression tools;
-allow for the larger boundary of map version 160812.

For information about maps, cf. https://indico.cern.ch/event/642366/contributions/2606389/ .
